# Vault: the published editor files and their hashes must be byte-for-byte
# identical on every platform. Treat them as binary so git never converts
# line endings (CRLF<->LF), which would change their bytes and break the
# SHA-256 verification the project depends on.
public/pdf-editor-lean.html      -text
public/pdf-editor-ocr-fast.html  -text
public/pdf-editor-ocr-full.html  -text
public/index.html                -text
public/SHA256SUMS.txt            -text
